title: L1SpawnLore
position: 74,-25
color: blue
---
<<actor ActorScreen 0 "happy">>
Harmony: Indulge me.
<<actor ActorScreen 1 "happy" false>>
Abaddon: You, my little flower, have died, and worst of all, your soul has been shunned by the grace of god.
Harmony: I figured! Endless torment and smell of sulphur probably means I'm in Hell!
Abaddon: Yes, but you have awoken...
Abaddon: [imp] Something or someone[/imp] has planted a seed...
Abaddon: In the form of that weapon you're holding. 
Abaddon: [imp] The Flower of Hell. [/imp]
Harmony: Well thanks, something or someone! 
Harmony: I won't stick around to find out why though, I'm getting out of here!
Abaddon: An undead vessel won't be let to walk in the gardens of man, little flower...
<<actor ActorScreen 0 "sad">>
Harmony: How do I fix that?
<<actor ActorScreen 1 "forlorn" false>>
Abaddon: You can not, little flower.
<<actor ActorScreen 0 "happy">>
Harmony: Betchya this handy dandy gun can!
Abaddon: Do not be foolish now... 
Abaddon: And put some respect on [imp]The Flower of Hell. [/imp]
Harmony: If I'm undead now.. and my gun kills undead things... I bet I could figure something out!
Abaddon: Erhh... I guess you do have a point...
<<actor ActorScreen 0 "evil">>
Harmony: Of course I do. 
Harmony: With guns and violence, you can make the whole world turn!
Abaddon: I don't know if that works down here...
<<hideAll ActorScreen>>
<<end LineView>>
