title: L1Library
position: -615,86
color: yellow
---
<<start LineView>>
<<actor ActorScreen 0 "happy">>
<<actor ActorScreen 1 "happy" false>>
Abbot: Question, Little flower. 
Harmony: Yes?
Abbot: I have overseen the wastes of hell, for far longer than the first soul wandered here.
Abbot: I have seen a few souls muster up the spite, to move their old bodies. 
Abbot: But not one has come with a weapon. Who or what gave it to you.
Harmony: Oh, I don't know. I thought you would know with your whole, thing goin' on.
Abbot: Thing?
Harmony: You look ancient and all knowing.  
Abbot: I simply write down, what happens in the Wastes of Hell. It's what I've always done. 
Harmony: So you a devil or what, you work for Satan?
Abbot: Hah, him.. Let's just say, I'm just curious.
Harmony: Shady, you sure are lucky shooting you just makes you talk.
<<hideAll ActorScreen>>
<<end LineView>>
